## May 2019 Ballot Comment: Update subscring word to subscribing

Submitted by Ricardo Quintano Neira
Chapter/section: Overview
Url: https://fhircast.hl7.org/specification/May2019Ballot/index.html
Type: A-T

Summary: Update subscring word to subscribing

Comment: Update subscring word to subscribing

Existing wording: The subscring app may query a session's current context and initiate context changes by accessing APIs exposed by the Hub.
Proposed wording: The subscribing app may query a session's current context and initiate context changes by accessing APIs exposed by the Hub.
